title: Print, "Plate in Nouveaux Livre de Paysages (New Book of Landscapes)", ca. 1700
medium: Etching and engraving on white laid paper
signed: Signed in plate, lower right: D. Marot, avec Privilege.
creditline: Museum purchase from General Acquisitions Endowment Fund
description: In the foreground, a large tree provides shade for two figures playing with a dog, and an amphora. In the background, an arcade with niches, a body of water, and more figures with a dog.
